## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all technological impacts on teamwork. The rapid pace of technological change means that new developments could further alter team dynamics in ways not covered in this report. Additionally, the effectiveness of technology in enhancing teamwork can vary significantly across different organizational contexts and industries.

